cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

This paper is about designing recurrent neural networks using an evolutionary strategy-based algorithm. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also discusses the use of automatic hyperparameter optimization methods, which falls under the sub-categories cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper mentions the application of recurrent networks in prediction problems, which is relevant to cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
